\n<Kobold Archer>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Away with you!!\.\. Only kobolds will pass through here!\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]

Neneko turns towards the familiar figure as it quickly dashes on the weird,\. thick,\. cobwebs.
\n<\n[1]>This is bad...\.\.\. she's going to get in trouble if this keeps up...
\n<Kobold Archer>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>You want passage?\.\. Then bring me food!\.\. FOOD!\.\. I'm hungry!\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\n[1]>!?\.\. What!?\.\. What's that smirk,\. you mocking me,\. lizard?
\n<\n[1]>Free food?\.\. You think I'm having it easy?!\.\. Hmph...
The lizard boy point at it's open maw.\.\.
\n<Kobold Archer>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Our village is ahead!\.\. Go on,\. good kitten!\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<???>Shshsh!\.\. She oughta pass from here if she's going down!
A hooded figure stands by the cliff.\.\.
It seems to be waiting for someone,\. certain they wouldn't miss it by standing there,\. right outside of the dwarven territory.
\^\n<Neneko>Tch...\.\.\. how did you...?!\.\. No human can hear me come...\.\.\.\.\.
\n<???>Human?!\.\. Nyohoho,\. human I'm not,\. you silly!
\n<???>Yes!\.\. That was good!\.\. Sexy!\.\. Lewd catgirls go a long way!\.\. That could help you get deep in the Hole!!
\n<Neneko>Wait a minute,\. "performance"?\.\. "Sexy"?\.\. Just what are you talking aaa\BST[6]aaAAAAAAAA!
\n<Neneko>Y-\.y-\.you pervert!!\.\. \BST[3]Who told you you could look?!\.\. I'll make sure you won't spill the beans!!
\n<???>Now now,\. there's nothing wrong with it!\.\. Nothing at all!\.\. A young catgirl has her...\.\.\. instincts!\.\. Believe me,\. I would know.
\n<???>Rather,\. you're pretty skilled!\.\. Don't you want to get your little brother back?\.\.
\n<Neneko>!!\.\. \BST[7]How do you know about him?\.\. You're not with the ones that took him,\. are you?!
\n<???>Nyo nyo nyo,\. they're already far from here,\. I'm afraid!
\n<Black Cat>You can call me "Black Cat",\. miss Neneko.\.\. We have much to discuss!
\n<Neneko>What now?\.\. Am not interested,\. leave me alone...
\n<Black Cat>Sorry,\. I had to,\. so you could understand the power that's within your grasp.
\n<Black Cat>Master the \c[18]Neko Lures\c[0],\. as your gifted body can channel Mana by many means.\.\. Show off your youthful body,\. and no road will remain closed to you,\. child.
\n<Black Cat>Your power has always been with you,\. you needed but to ask.
Press \i[588] to switch between the Item and Lure bar!
The \i[547] and \i[562] buttons can be used to select your Lure and to use it on the surrounding enemies or characters!
During fights,\. wait for a sign that your enemy is vulnerable,\. then STRIKE the right NEKO LURE!
\n<Neneko>That "Black Cat"...\.\.\. is she gone?\.\. Such energy just by showing off her...\.\.\.
\n<Neneko>I went out cold...\.\.\. Can I even do something like that?\.\. \BST[1]That would make my life much easier...
\n<Neneko>I-\.I need to find weak enemies to test this new "power" out...
\n<Dwarf Axeman>Aye aye,\. going back to ta Fortress?
\n<Dwarf Archer>I can snipe a lizard's head from over \fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>100 steps\fn<GameFont>\fs[30].\.\. Been training all me life fer that.
